{
  "stem": "3933.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because he belonged to the-- Polish underground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that's another story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, we have to get rid of her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You want to be killed?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have also a son.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want any, nothing to do with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm sorry, she has to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She has to leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, God, and she, in the morning, she says, Mary-- oh.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In mean time, he wasn't there, Kola.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When they started this-- this terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went to, I said-- I told him, he went to my brother-in-law to see what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the way, they weren't in ghetto inside, [INAUDIBLE] they weren't in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of my husband's sister, Smitzel, her husband were not-- they did not have obligation to live in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why, you're going to ask?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he wasn't Jewish, her husband.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a different story, he wasn't Jewish but he converted, whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were out of the ghetto, so far.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I call, I send him there, Kola, to some-- find out what happened to them-- the old lady, my mother-in-law and they were all there again.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the old lady, my mother-in-law was sitting, maybe she wasn't crying after me, she was crying after her little boy, of my son.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know about me, whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They weren't very, terribly happy when he married me, because I was very poor, and very broken home, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then he said, Mary and the baby is at my place, and she is-- they was terribly happy and glad.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my brother gave him, the non-Jewish brother-in-law, gave him some money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In meantime, when he wasn't there she said, Lucia, Mary, I'm going to give you a peasant old dress, an old skirt, a long skirt.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
